Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetmanager.server.spring

Class DataAssetExchangeResource

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetmanager.server.spring.DataAssetExchangeResource
@RestController @RequestMapping("/servers/{serverName}/open-metadata/access-services/asset-manager/users/{userId}") public class DataAssetExchangeResource extends Object
DataAssetExchangeResource is the server-side implementation of the Asset Manager OMAS's support for data asset such as data sets. It matches the DataAssetExchangeClient.
